name: Aus DeFi NFT Heroes - The Creator

metadata.name: Aus DeFi NFT Heroes - The Creator #1/33
metadata.description: The creator is full of ideas. Every day, new ones pop into her head. Cut her in half and all you see is creativity. Sheâ€™s embraced web3 culture and sees the world the same as Neo, looking at code in The Matrix. The world, in her eyes, is full of inefficiencies. Bogged down by slow and manual processes and a massive lack of transparency. She aims to change the world for the better and will explain her ideas in detail if you give her the time. Unashamedly, she is a dreamer that wants to leave the world in a better place. Unlike some of her web2 counterparts, she has embraced building in the open because she knows that ideas are aplenty, and execution is key.
